  "response": "As of October 2023, here are some of the best mobile phones under \u20b915,000 in India, known for their good performance, camera quality, and overall value for money:\n\n1. **Realme Narzo 50**:\n   - Display: 6.6-inch FHD+ IPS LCD\n   - Processor: MediaTek Helio G96\n   - RAM: Up to 6GB\n   - Storage: Up to 128GB\n   - Camera: 50MP main, 2MP macro, 2MP depth sensor; 16MP front camera\n   - Battery: 5000mAh with 33W fast charging\n\n2. **Redmi Note 10**:\n   - Display: 6.43-inch FHD+ AMOLED\n   - Processor: Qualcomm Snapdragon 678\n   - RAM: Up to 6GB\n   - Storage: Up to 128GB\n   - Camera: 48MP main, 8MP ultra-wide, 2MP macro, 2MP depth sensor; 13MP front camera\n   - Battery: 5000mAh with 33W fast charging\n\n3. **Samsung Galaxy M32**:\n   - Display: 6.4-inch FHD+ Super AMOLED, 90Hz refresh rate\n   - Processor: MediaTek Helio G80\n   - RAM: Up to 6GB\n   - Storage: Up to 128GB\n   - Camera: 64MP main, 8MP ultra-wide, 2MP macro, 2MP depth sensor; 20MP front camera\n   - Battery: 6000mAh with 15W charging\n\n4. **Poco M3 Pro 5G**:\n   - Display: 6.5-inch FHD+ IPS LCD, 90Hz refresh rate\n   - Processor: MediaTek Dimensity 700\n   - RAM: Up to 6GB\n   - Storage: Up to 128GB\n   - Camera: 48MP main, 2MP macro, 2MP depth sensor; 8MP front camera\n   - Battery: 5000mAh with 18W fast charging\n\n5. **Motorola Moto G40 Fusion**:\n   - Display: 6.8-inch FHD+ IPS LCD, 120Hz refresh rate\n   - Processor: Qualcomm Snapdragon 732G\n   - RAM: Up to 6GB\n   - Storage: Up to 128GB\n   - Camera: 64MP main, 8MP ultra-wide, 2MP depth sensor; 16MP front camera\n   - Battery: 6000mAh with 20W fast charging\n\nThese options provide a good balance of performance, camera quality, battery life, and display features, making them great choices in the sub-\u20b915,000 price segment.",
